{"tid":2213418,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李子賢媽媽給兒子的親筆信：你選擇條路好難行 以你為榮！","createTime":"2020-09-22T13:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T04:52:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"57ce26c571f4db88bdfc01d5bf18e15cdac0b914","tid":2213418,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/26TD-OXKZK6m_wPsRvsdviLlX9I=/802x1006/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FM3RRINZSJHDXJE4IIGWHGENXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F26TD-OXKZK6m_wPsRvsdviLlX9I%3D%2F802x1006%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFM3RRINZSJHDXJE4IIGWHGENXA.jpg&h=9cbd22a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「你好嗎？媽咪好掛住你呀，你幾時返嚟呀？」兒子失蹤25日，為母的怎會不掛心？一封寫於9月16日給兒子的信，李子賢媽媽難過又堅強，邊嘆：「你份人就係太大愛，下下都諗人，有時我真係想你自私啲諗下自己」，邊撐：「無論將來如何，你都係我嘅寶貝仔，媽咪以你為榮。」<br />\n<br />\n今年中秋未必人月兩團圓，李媽媽望月只有一素願：「求下有冇好心人幫下我，救番你。」<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一封李子賢媽媽親筆寫給兒子的信，寫於9月16日星期三、即特首林鄭月娥於行會前堅稱由內地司法機關處理12人案件是「恰當做法」的翌日，也是12人失蹤第25日。<br />\n<br />\n曾經自言食叉燒飯也會惦念兒子正在吃甚麼的李媽媽，在抬頭單字寫「仔」的信中寫道：「自從唔見咗你，我日日都失眠，有時諗下又喊，諗下又喊」；執筆於兒子音訊全無第25日，李媽媽坦言每天自我重複的一句是「要堅強」，「呀仔，等我救呀，唔可以跌低，只要（可）向前行」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/EETBNGIDOBHR7ENQHI3X6GSK4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FEETBNGIDOBHR7ENQHI3X6GSK4Q%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I29iuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=63beabb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FEETBNGIDOBHR7ENQHI3X6GSK4Q%2F&h=f1f36617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/EETBNGIDOBHR7ENQHI3X6GSK4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"e9223cc91bdf12864b860a5857f9007c139a192f","tid":2213418,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eff273034a5f4eb6f1a6255c413efb087c8c55","tid":2213418,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2fbe3f7d0cfc9c9bff1f77c25f047fa5f1f0dc","tid":2213418,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446d17964b92c5ac6519fb6f162da31ec46fa43b","tid":2213418,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69069d0e7dfb8b634ece15f0e19ebafed4a6c84a","tid":2213418,"uid":1623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f72fb1230594158ddb6739ad438c7c665ea8759","tid":2213418,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0